detaileddescription.para: The EnergyDiff is owned by the caller if the EnergyDiff::toTriples method is NOT used. When toTriples() is used, the nodes that create the EnergyDiff are "given" to the Triples object, which automatically destroys them at the right time.
Most of the time, users will not have to remember to free the EnergyDiff themselves as the toTriples method is always used.
